data.description: Big Price reduction For a Quick Sale!. This 4 Bedrooms and 3.5 Bathrooms Beautiful Home is Located in Coquina at Maple Ridge, Ave Maria, Florida with over 2,251 sq. ft in Living Areas and 1 Car Garage. Posses a Magnificent Master Bedroom and Master Bathroom on the First Floor. Upstairs, are 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, a Loft and the Laundry. The Patio Area has a spectacular View of the Lake with a Lanai paved with beautiful bricks and a Relaxing Area to Enjoy!. The Home is Located in the Small Town of Ave Maria, with an University (Ave Maria University); With Shops, Restaurants, a Publix Supermarket, Parks, Community Club House, and many more amenities. This Home is a Marble, Hurry!.
